og.description: The 2015 Lincoln Heritage Water Trail's third annual Abe's River Race took place on Saturday, May 23, 2015, along a 13.5 mile route of the north-flowing Sangamon River between the start at Irwin Bridge and the finish at Petersburg's Riverside Park. Race director Scott Hewitt said about 60 boats were registered.
og.title: Photos: Abe's River Race
